articles.title: Taiwan leader's meeting with McCarthy could provoke a 'big' reaction from China, says analyst - CNBC
articles.description: A meeting between Taiwan's leader and U.S. House Speaker will provoke a strong reaction from China, said Anna Ashton, China director at the Eurasia Group.
